quests.desc: Welcome to TextWorld! Here is your task for today. Your first objective is to open the chest drawer. Once you have pulled open the chest drawer, take the old key from the chest drawer. After that, check that the wooden door is unlocked with the old key. After unlocking the wooden door, open the wooden door. After that, make an effort to travel east. After that, ensure that the screen door in the kitchen is open. After that, venture east. After that, make an attempt to go to the south. And then, take the carrot that's in the garden. And once you've done that, you win!
commands: take old key from chest drawer
unlock wooden door with old key

Well, here we are in a kitchen.

 You can make out [if c_2 is locked]a locked[else if c_2 is open]an opened[otherwise]a closed[end if] refrigerator.[if c_2 is open and there is something in the c_2] The refrigerator contains [a list of things in the c_2].[end if][if c_2 is open and the c_2 contains nothing] The refrigerator is empty! What a waste of a day![end if] You can make out a counter. The counter is usual.[if there is something on the s_1] On the counter you see [a list of things on the s_1].[end if][if there is nothing on the s_1] But the thing is empty, unfortunately.[end if] You see a stove. Make a note of this, you might have to put stuff on or in it later on. [if there is something on the s_2]You see [a list of things on the s_2] on the stove.[end if][if there is nothing on the s_2]Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. infos.name: bedroom
infos.desc:
I never took you for the sort of person who would show up in a bedroom, but I guess I was wrong. You begin looking for stuff.

 You make out a chest drawer.[if c_0 is open and there is something in the c_0] The chest drawer contains [a list of things in the c_0].[end if][if c_0 is open and the c_0 contains nothing] Empty! Suddenly, you bump your head on the ceiling, but it's not such a bad bump that it's going to prevent you from looking at objects and even things.[end if][if c_1 is open and the c_1 contains nothing] What a letdown! The antique trunk is empty![end if] You hear a noise behind you and spin around, but you can't see anything other than a king-size bed!
